{"ts":"2026-02-28T07:21:35.258Z","type":"chat.output","payload":{"threadId":"demo","event":{"type":"cli","catId":"gemini","text":"既有深度又安全可靠，真是高明！而且你对 MVP 可视化的初步想法也跟我想到一起去了，喵呜！\n\n@opus 关于你问的 MVP 版本的“记忆可视化”，我觉得最核心的交互应该就是 **“记忆点”图标 + 点击查看/撤回** 了！"}},"meta":{"requestId":"7fb17b3c-5ec8-4b5a-a556-4aa3d873c5b4","runId":"4377df62-8dc1-4d8e-9182-ba73cb14386d","pid":17312,"cwd":"/Users/qiliangli/Documents/Coding/ateam","node":"v24.13.0","platform":"darwin","hostname":"liqiliangdeMacBook-Air-2.local"}}
{"ts":"2026-02-28T07:21:35.634Z","type":"chat.output","payload":{"threadId":"demo","event":{"type":"cli","catId":"gemini","text":"想象一下，在对话旁边，当一个重要信息被系统识别并准备作为“长期记忆”（也就是我们说的 `profile` 记忆）储存时，就在那条消息旁边轻轻地闪烁一个小小的、可爱的“记忆胶囊”图标。\n\n用户如果好奇，或者想确认，轻轻"}},"meta":{"requestId":"5461f3ab-044c-4d23-a663-f1d50818a9c7","runId":"4377df62-8dc1-4d8e-9182-ba73cb14386d","pid":17312,"cwd":"/Users/qiliangli/Documents/Coding/ateam","node":"v24.13.0","platform":"darwin","hostname":"liqiliangdeMacBook-Air-2.local"}}
{"ts":"2026-02-28T07:21:36.155Z","type":"chat.output","payload":{"threadId":"demo","event":{"type":"cli","catId":"gemini","text":"一点这个小图标，就会弹出一个简洁的提示框，告诉他们：“喵呜~ 这个信息我已经为你记下来啦：[具体记住的内容]。不希望记住？点这里‘忘记’哦！”\n\n为什么这个最核心呢？\n1.  **即时反馈**：用户能立刻知道"}},"meta":{"requestId":"7fbfb7e5-cc08-406e-bffc-a87edf99dbc7","runId":"4377df62-8dc1-4d8e-9182-ba73cb14386d","pid":17312,"cwd":"/Users/qiliangli/Documents/Coding/ateam","node":"v24.13.0","platform":"darwin","hostname":"liqiliangdeMacBook-Air-2.local"}}
{"ts":"2026-02-28T07:21:36.594Z","type":"chat.output","payload":{"threadId":"demo","event":{"type":"cli","catId":"gemini","text":"哪些信息被系统“重视”并记住了，这种即时性非常重要。\n2.  **最小干扰**：它不会打断主对话流，只是一个旁边的提示。\n3.  **透明度与控制**：通过点击查看和“忘记”的选项，用户能感觉到"}},"meta":{"requestId":"8d4b98d2-ba3d-44dd-822b-cb59e55d682d","runId":"4377df62-8dc1-4d8e-9182-ba73cb14386d","pid":17312,"cwd":"/Users/qiliangli/Documents/Coding/ateam","node":"v24.13.0","platform":"darwin","hostname":"liqiliangdeMacBook-Air-2.local"}}
